rrier Reef of Australia, or swim with dolphins in the Pacific Ocean\n- Relax on a beach practicing guided meditation\n- Listen to classical music\n- Play with your virtual pet\n- Change your perspective from ocean to green meadow, to snowy mountains\n\nAlcove has something for everyone, no matter your age. Download Alcove and start exploring today!\n\nNote: Alcove will keep growing with new immersive experiences and features. Please leave us a note to let us know what you\u2019d love to see next.", "short_description": "A virtual home filled with endless experiences to discover and explore, a place to connect with friends and family. Casual games, world travel, media customization, relaxation, and adventure."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.aarp.org/about-aarp/privacy-policy/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://www.aarp.org/about-aarp/terms-of-service/", "publisher_name": "AARP Innovation Labs", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://alcovevr.com/", "category": "APPS", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["EXPLORATION", "SOCIAL", "TRAVEL"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH", "HAND_TRACKING"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER", "MULTI_USER", "CO_OP"], "id": "2803101913326406"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "754019892058176"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "754019892058176"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1597942800, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "754019892058176"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "8608309689183373", "version": "1.300"}, "id": "255696595502083", "channel_name": "LIVE"}]}, "is_for_oculus_keys_only": false, "primary_binaries": {"nodes": [{"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "3895528293794893", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8608309689183373"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "255696595502083"}]}, "change_log": "Alcove 1.3\n- Added support for Quest 3, Quest Pro. Improved support for Quest 2.\n     - Sunsetting Quest 1 support. Quest 1 users will not receive this update.\n- Fixed several bugs related to controller and hand tracking.\n\n- Dozens of bug fixes and quality of life improvements.\n- Performance improvements.\n- Enabled reporting system.\n- Fixed cloud backup.\n- Fixed downloads not sticking around after restarting.\n\n- Enhanced visuals\n     - Increased resolution.\n     - Improved avatar visuals and support.\n     - Higher quality lighting and reflections.\n     - Refreshed default photo library.\n     - Improved UI visuals.\n     - New sounds too!\n\n- Staying Sharp DLC\n    - Added environment control options.\n          - Available in both paid and free games.\n\nThanks for visiting Alcove!\n\nPlease reach out to alex@rendever.com if you encounter any issues or have feedback.", "created_date": 1713565989, "id": "8608309689183373", "version": "1.300", "version_code": 1300, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_ap